text.0: In his first interview since Election Day, President Trump recapped baseless, false and misleading claims he has made before of a “rigged” election. Get the facts. https://t.co/CRYGJqTOnq #FactCHAT
text.1: The Trump campaign presented limited, selective parts of surveillance camera footage to make the false claim that poll workers in Georgia brought thousands of illegal ballots into an Atlanta facility on election night in suspicious “suitcases.” https://t.co/Ef8OqYoCJJ #FactCHAT
